## Project-Specific Rules

### Component Structure
- Use semantic domain naming: `components/prototypes/[domain]/[component]`
- Extract reusable components to appropriate directories
- Document component purpose and semantic domain in comments

### Styling
- Use TailwindCSS with scorecard theme colors
- Follow existing scorecard aesthetic (`#556b2f`, `#8b956d`, etc.)
- Maintain responsive design patterns

### TypeScript
- Use strict typing
- Define types in `/types` directory
- Export interfaces for component props

### React/Next.js
- Use "use client" for interactive components
- Prefer server components when possible
- Handle SSR/hydration carefully (see fog visualization for examples)

